fields.title: Two slight improvement for custom UserService: - try userRealm as a file only if class is not found, other exeptions are real error - log userService only after setup, for better logging, as it can use gitblit.properties for custom .toString
Two slight improvement for custom UserService
fields.body:
Two slight improvement for custom UserService

- try userRealm as a file only if class is not found, other exceptions are real error
- log userService only after setup, for better logging, as it can use gitblit.properties for custom .toString
